*"On je izjavio da će ostati."* (He declared that he would stay.)
*"Ona je izjavila da je spremna da pomogne."* (She stated that she was ready to help.)
*"Želeo je da dostavi izjavu o svojoj situaciji."* (He wanted to submit a statement about his situation.)
*"On je dao izjavu u kojoj je objasnio svoje postupke."* (He gave a statement in which he explained his actions.)
*"Nadležni su tražili od njega da dostavi izjavu."* (The authorities asked him to submit a statement.)